data.description: Rustic farmhouse style with beautiful details in the Village at Wicklow! Split 4 bedroom home includes vintage hardwoods, exposed beams, gourmet appliances, whole house water softener, instant hot water to every room, and high efficiency mechanicals.  The welcoming kitchen features granite countertops, walk-in pantry, counter-height seating, plus area for a table or gathering space.  Large bonus room is fully finished with extra temperature control and easy access to floored attic storage.  Don't miss the huge master closet, screened-in porch, tornado shelter, newer Pella windows, and whole house generator. If all of these conveniences aren't enough, character and charm will impress throughout the home with faux brick finishes and tromp l'oeil masterfully created by renowned artist, Sheila Renfro.
data.whatILove: The wood floors and beams are reclaimed and add so much character for that perfect rustic look.  Such a friendly neighborhood with great family amenities too!
